<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Home</title>
    <%- include('partials/loggedout-navbar.ejs'); %>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="row block">
        <img class="block-image col-md-6 offset-lg-1" src="img/signup.png" alt="signup">
        <div class="col-md-6 block-content">
          <h5>If you want to use the web app personally then it is the right time to signup to Mirror through the signup page</h5>
          <p>Go to SignIn(top-right) -> Click the link saying 'No account yet? Create one here' -> Enter your details -> Takes you to signin page. SignIn and enjoy recollecting your memories</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row block">
        <div class="col-md-6 block-content">
          <h5>Have an account already? Then go to the signin page to access Mirror</h5>
          <p>Go to SignIn(top-right) -> Enter your mailid and password</p>
        </div>
        <img class="block-image col-md-6 offset-lg-1" src="img/signin.png" alt="signin">
      </div>
      <div class="row block">
        <img class="block-image col-md-6 offset-lg-1" src="img/memories.png" alt="memories">
        <div class="col-md-6 block-content">
          <h5>See all your memories at a single place, add them, edit them, delete them, view them and anything you want</h5>
          <p>SignIn -> Click on Home to view all your memories</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row block">
        <div class="col-md-6 block-content">
          <h5>View your whole beautiful memory</h5>
          <p>SignIn -> On the memory block click on the link saying 'Display Full Memory'</p>
        </div>
        <img class="block-image col-md-6 offset-lg-1" src="img/display.png" alt="display">
      </div>
      <div class="row block">
        <img class="block-image col-md-6 offset-lg-1" src="img/add.png" alt="add">
        <div class="col-md-6 block-content">
          <h5>Have something memorable/ boring/ normal worth remembering? Go ahead and add them in your daily memories!</h5>
          <p>SignIn -> Click the plus(+) icon at the bottom-right of the memories page -> Takes you to the new page. Add your memory there</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row block">
        <div class="col-md-6 block-content">
          <h5>Missed out noting something in a precious memory? Go and edit it right now</h5>
          <p>SignIn -> Click the little pencil icon on the memory block -> Takes you to the edit page. Edit it and save your renwed memory</p>
        </div>
        <img class="block-image col-md-6 offset-lg-1" src="img/edit.png" alt="edit">
      </div>
      <div class="row block">
        <img class="block-image col-md-6 offset-lg-1" src="img/delete.png" alt="delete">
        <div class="col-md-6 block-content">
          <h5>Want to delete any chasing/ bad memory. Just do it in 2 steps</h5>
          <p>SignIn -> Click the little trash icon on the memory block</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row block">
        <div class="col-md-6 block-content">
          <h5>Have any issue with the website? Or want to give some feedback regarding the website.</h5>
          <p>Go to Contact Us(top-right) -> Fill out the form and we will reach you out within no time</p>
        </div>
        <img class="block-image col-md-6 offset-lg-1" src="img/contact.png" alt="contact">
      </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-IQsoLXl5PILFhosVNubq5LC7Qb9DXgDA9i+tQ8Zj3iwWAwPtgFTxbJ8NT4GN1R8p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.1/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-Atwg2Pkwv9vp0ygtn1JAojH0nYbwNJLPhwyoVbhoPwBhjQPR5VtM2+xf0Uwh9KtT" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="js/password-toggle.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
